---
title: Cajun Summer Feast with Grilled Corn and Green Peppers
description: Get ready for a Cajun-inspired cookout! Spiced BBQ chicken, Old Bay butter-basted corn and fire-roasted green peppers celebrate the humble summer cookout like no other! Bacon, green onion, and sour cream topped potatoes are the perfect long-weekend side!
